    "title": "彼得後書 1:1–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001001-61001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108572\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">彼得</span>所寫信給的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108077\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">信徒們</span>已經領受了<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108043\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">好消息</span>。他們已經從<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108215\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">世界</span>的罪惡中被拯救出來。<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108199\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">神</span>已經賜給他們效法<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108219\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">耶穌</span>的榜樣所需的一切。他們可以像耶穌一樣活出敬虔和<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108361\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">聖潔</span>的生命。他們需要在<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108232\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">信心</span>上不斷學習和成長。彼得明確指出這需要努力和辛勤的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108208\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">工作</span>。他列出了信徒應該不斷成長的七個方面。這個列表類似於<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108102\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">保羅</span>在加拉太書5:22–23中列出的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108154\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">聖靈的果子</span>。當信徒越來越多認識耶穌，他們會變得越來越像祂。這就是他們分享神的本性的方式。在信心上成長能使得信徒在耶穌的國度在地上擴展時發揮作用。耶穌的國度就是<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108561\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">神的國</span>。</p>",
